<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Lab 3.6 — Hybrid + rerank
Dense (voyage-3) + BM25 (rank_bm25) + RRF + Cohere rerank-v3.5.
Reuses 03-naive-rag corpus + eval questions.
Cost: ~$0.10 (Cohere rerank is ~$1/1000 searches).</cell id="cell-0">
